{"tid":927803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[識波撚入]究竟要幾撚識波先會覺得今年基沙文係有世三乃至金球","createTime":"2018-12-04T11:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T06:43:50.000Z","uid":45335,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2fdf36813f6dc5560ea1036eb714bd5d5d8f99c6","tid":927803,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"原本以為得child登幾條傻鳩係咁捧基沙文<br />\n點知今日見到原來佢自己覺得覺得自己deserve金球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再睇返d記者排名 屌你有成堆都排佢有頭三乃至第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返上季佢歐聯打得廢比人踢左落去霸氣杯 係玩哂呀但有少少挑戰性既球隊都冇<br />\n<br />\n聯賽打西超隊首席射手又連廿球都冇<br />\n<br />\n世杯未至於平凡既 正常above average比你班死忠決賽好少少就講到carry咁 入得三球咋傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全年講緊2x+1x 同丁力差唔多當自己球王呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c306df68415327ca4b5f3e8a9602aed231d62cbf","tid":927803,"uid":45335,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:46:33.000Z","msg":"如果唔係拎左世杯 世10都冇你份呀歐霸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1c82ef0d1537b7bb9aa89e400dd973782e1217","tid":927803,"uid":45335,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯原來有4球<br />\n其中3球12碼咁巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2159cabc0acbbcd2c9186a351b229c4189cde5","tid":927803,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c306df68415327ca4b5f3e8a9602aed231d62cbf","tid":927803,"uid":45335,"